title.narrative: BIRTH REGISTRATION

description.narrative: More children under 5 have a birth certificate in Tanzania Mainland, which contributes to Access To Justice, Access To Justice (Covid), Birth Registration, Harmful Practices (Fgm/C And Child Marriage). UNICEF aims to achieve this through Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: Girls and boys have access to and are better served by a national child protection system that prevents and responds to physical, sexual,and emotional violence, abuse, neglect, exploitation, harmful social practices and ensures access to adequate adult care across the lifecycle (young child, early adolescent, late adolescent)
